                              =========
                               Rx Ctrl
                              =========

Abstract:
~~~~~~~~~
Rx ctrl is a controller that generates DMA transfer request for incoming
packets. These are transfered from on-card memory to host RAM. Memory locations
in host RAM are described by descriptors supplied by descriptor download
manager. Informations about packet transfer are sent to status update manager.

Author:
~~~~~~~
Petr Kastovsky <kastosky@liberouter.org>


